ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a70c3fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=7b827526\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a814bf0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=0d47ab9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=55883399\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/